p Subjects
p What are subjects? Subjects are classes of entities could be grouped under a category. Subjects work similarly to tags.  You can create subjects categories when you are transcribing pages or after you have transcribed them by going into a collection and selecting the subjects tab.
p How do I create URL links for subjects?  While transcribing, you can use double square brackets to create URL links for subjects.  [[Jane Doe]] will link the text "Jane Doe" to the subject Jane Doe, while [[Jane Doe]Jane] will link the text Jane to the subject Jane Doe.
